plot: MTV presents its Video Music Awards for 2001. Performers include U2, *NSYNC (with Michael Jackson), Staind, Alicia Keys, Jennifer Lopez (with Ja Rule), and Missy Elliott (with Nelly Furtado).
title: MTV Video Music Awards 2001
